name: Executioner Charles-Henri Sanson (ZBond X1)
description:
Each ZBond X alludes to a specific part of mortality from the past, present and future and is the initial investment for a corresponding Death Zollar.
 
ZBond X1 is part of the Z Mortality Monetary System which abandons the idea of numerical currency by instead asking the ZBond owner to apply a personal interpretation of how much we value different aspects of mortality. 

How much is death worth to you and yours? 

Created and issued by Zederal Reserve. 
Part of the ZEconomy.
